INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2,1,'2012-05-30 18:06:33','2012-05-30 18:06:33','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n\r\n...or something like this:\r\n\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\n\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','trash','open','open','','sample-page','','','2012-09-24 14:31:47','2012-09-24 14:31:47','',0,'http://__DOMAIN__/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(8,1,'2012-05-30 18:27:58','2012-05-30 18:27:58','Once you’re in your Admin, The About Us page can be edited by clicking on the “Pages” tab located on the left side of the website under Dashboard. You should then hover over the page you want to edit; four options will appear under the page title and click the “Edit” tab. After you’re on the About Us edit page, click on the box that says “About Us Content Here” to start adding content to your page. \r\n\r\nThe About Us page can include anything about your business. A few things to consider explaining on this page include who you are, how your business got started, and where you are located.\r\n','About Us','','publish','open','open','','about-us','','','2012-06-29 13:08:45','2012-06-29 13:08:45','',0,'http://__DOMAIN__/?page_id=8',0,'page','',0),(9,1,'2012-05-30 18:27:54','2012-05-30 18:27:54','','About Us','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision','','','2012-05-30 18:27:54','2012-05-30 18:27:54','',8,'http://__DOMAIN__/?p=9',0,'revision','',0),(10,1,'2012-05-30 18:28:18','2012-05-30 18:28:18','<strong>Jim Smith</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Expert-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-55\" title=\"Expert-2\" src=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Expert-2-118x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"118\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n\r\nJim Smith is the Founder and CEO of Website Enterprise. Smith is dedicated to creating powerful and effective websites. He has been in the Internet industry for over 45 years and has created over a million sites.\r\n\r\nBefore opening Website Enterprise, Smith was a lead Programmer for Writ’s Design. Smith had ambition to start his own website building company and left to make that dream reality.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Greg Hemingway</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Expert-3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-56\" title=\"Expert-3\" src=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Expert-3-118x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"118\" height=\"150\" /></a>\r\n\r\nGreg Hemingway is President of Programming and Design. He started off in the company 30 years ago as an entry-level programmer and has moved up from there.\r\n\r\nSince becoming President of Programming and Design in 2005, he has been responsible for leading a design team that has become widely recognized with numerous design awards\r\n\r\nHemmingway holds a Bachelor of Arts and a Master’s degree in Web Design and Development.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Sally Johnson</strong>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Expert-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-57\" title=\"Expert-1\" src=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Expert-1-118x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"118\" height=\"150\" /></a>Sally Johnson is Director of Marketing. Johnson has worked for Website Enterprise for 15 years.\r\n\r\nJohnson has a Bachelor’s in Public Relations and a Master’s degree in Direct Interactive Marketing. She has been proven an expert in her field through numerous successful campaigns.','Experts','','trash','open','open','','experts','','','2012-09-24 14:31:46','2012-09-24 14:31:46','',0,'http://__DOMAIN__/?page_id=10',0,'page','',0),(11,1,'2012-05-30 18:28:06','2012-05-30 18:28:06','','Experts','','inherit','open','open','','10-revision','','','2012-05-30 18:28:06','2012-05-30 18:28:06','',10,'http://__DOMAIN__/?p=11',0,'revision','',0),(12,1,'2012-05-30 18:28:34','2012-05-30 18:28:34','<a href=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Testimonial-3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-59\" title=\"Testimonial-3\" src=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Testimonial-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"114\" height=\"114\" /></a>“Outstanding company is all I can say. Everyone I worked with went above and beyond to make my website successful!”\r\n\r\n-James Matthew\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Testimonial-1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-60\" title=\"Testimonial-1\" src=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Testimonial-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"114\" height=\"114\" /></a>“I attribute my website’s success on this company. They created a visually effective and easy to navigate sight which my customers constantly comment on how much they love!”\r\n\r\n-Shannon Long\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Testimonial-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-61\" title=\"Testimonial-2\" src=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Testimonial-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"114\" height=\"114\" /></a>“I want to thank your company for your exemplary service and top-notch technology skills. Your website has created vital traffic for my company!”\r\n\r\n-Mark Swartz','Looks Who\'s Talking','','trash','open','open','','looks-whos-talking','','','2012-09-24 14:31:47','2012-09-24 14:31:47','',0,'http://__DOMAIN__/?page_id=12',0,'page','',0),(13,1,'2012-05-30 18:28:30','2012-05-30 18:28:30','','Looks Who\'s Talking','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision','','','2012-05-30 18:28:30','2012-05-30 18:28:30','',12,'http://__DOMAIN__/?p=13',0,'revision','',0),(14,1,'2012-05-30 18:28:45','2012-05-30 18:28:45','<a href=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/SBC-2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-64\" title=\"SBC (2)\" src=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/SBC-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"119\" height=\"119\" /></a><a href=\"http://sitebuildingcenter.com/\">SiteBuildingCenter</a> is a great resource to teach you how to use your website. Sitebuilding.com believes your website is the key to your success online, and they are dedicated to giving you the tools and tutorials you need to make your website successful.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/WP.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-65\" title=\"WP\" src=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/WP.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"119\" height=\"119\" /></a><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/WordPress_Lessons\">WordPress Tutorial</a> offers great resources to teach WordPress users how to use the program. The tutorials range from lessons for beginners to lessons on website development. No matter what you are trying to achieve with your WordPress, there is a tutorial to help you accomplish it!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/BH.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-66\" title=\"BH\" src=\"http://__DOMAIN__/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/BH.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"119\" height=\"119\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.brainhost.com/help/\">Brain Host</a> is dedicated to providing their customers with reliable, affordable hosting packages and world-class, 24/7 customer support. They understand how important your website is to your company’s success, which is why they promise a 99.9% uptime. No matter what your budget or hosting needs, Brain Host has a package for you.','Resources','','trash','open','open','','resources','','','2012-09-24 14:31:47','2012-09-24 14:31:47','',0,'http://__DOMAIN__/?page_id=14',0,'page','',0),(15,1,'2012-05-30 18:28:40','2012-05-30 18:28:40','','Resources','','inherit','open','open','','14-revision','','','2012-05-30 18:28:40','2012-05-30 18:28:40','',14,'http://__DOMAIN__/?p=15',0,'revision','',0),(16,1,'2012-05-30 18:29:02','2012-05-30 18:29:02','Feature your company or product on our website!\r\n\r\nThousands of people come to our site for information and advice on the industry. We have positioned ourselves as an expert in the field and love to share that knowledge with others.\r\n\r\nNow, you can share your service or company with our industry, too. We take pride in offering only the highest standards. If you feel you would be a good fit for our fans, please email us at advertise@myindustry.com for more information. \r\n','Advertise','','trash','open','open','','advertise','','','2012-09-24 14:31:46','2012-09-24 14:31:46','',0,'http://__DOMAIN__/?page_id=16',0,'page','',0),(17,1,'2012-05-30 18:28:55','2012-05-30 18:28:55','','Advertise','','inherit','open','open','','16-revision','','','2012-05-30 18:28:55','2012-05-30 18:28:55','',16,'http://__DOMAIN__/?p=17',0,'revision','',0),(18,1,'2012-05-30 18:29:39','2012-05-30 18:29:39','','Home','','publish','open','open','','home','','','2012-08-20 14:37:54','2012-08-20 14:37:54','',0,'http://__DOMAIN__/?p=18',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(19,1,'2012-05-30 18:29:39','2012-05-30 18:29:39',' ','','','publish','open','open','','19','','','2012-08-20 14:37:54','2012-08-